Package com.arjuna.ArjunaCommon.Template

Interface Summary
ListElement Items which are required to be put in some lists must implement this interface.
OrderedListElement Entries in OrderedLists must inherit from this class and define the specified methods.
 

Class Summary
BasicList A BasicList extends the concept of a SimpleList by searching and storing entries based upon their Uids.
BasicListIterator An iterator for BasicLists.
HashList This hash table for objects which define get_uid does not use the Java Hashtable class, since we sometimes want to add multiple different values under the same key.
HashListIterator An iterator for HashLists.
KeyedList  
ListElementWrapper For those objects which cannot provide get_uid, but which need to be added to a list.
OrderedList An ordered list stores items in an order defined by the objects themselves.
OrderedListIterator An iterator for OrderedLists.
SimpleList A SimpleList maintains entries in a linked list.
SimpleListIterator An iterator for SimpleLists.
